{"id": "4313", "revid": "54583845", "url": "https://hades.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4313", "title": "Deep Serpent", "text": "The Deep Serpent is a larger, more dangerous version of the &lt;a href=\"Sea-Serpent\"&gt;Sea-Serpent&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe Deep Serpent shares the same attack set as a Sea-Serpent, with a few key differences: their straight-line projectiles will split multiple times into smaller projectiles, and their arcing projectiles will cover the arena with many dangerous red zones at once, leaving very few safe spots. Their point-blank, 360 degree head sweep has a larger radius, as well.\nThe Deep Serpent appears as a mini-boss in &lt;a href=\"Oceanus\"&gt;Oceanus&lt;/a&gt;, accompanied by a large number of armored &lt;a href=\"Sop-Spindle\"&gt;Sop-Spindles&lt;/a&gt;."}
