{"id": "1052", "revid": "3510317", "url": "https://hades.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1052", "title": "Diamond", "text": "Diamonds are one of several &lt;a href=\"Artifacts\"&gt;Artifact&lt;/a&gt; currencies that can be earned within the Underworld. Along with &lt;a href=\"Titan%20Blood\"&gt;Titan Blood&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Ambrosia\"&gt;Ambrosia&lt;/a&gt;, they are a resource obtained via bounties. They can be used to purchase higher tier upgrades from the &lt;a href=\"House%20Contractor\"&gt;House Contractor&lt;/a&gt;, such as a Music Stand for listening to music, progressing character favors, or bonuses for picking up resources in escape attempts.\nDiamond Uses.\nDiamonds are used to:\nPurchasing every single thing from the contractor and fully upgrading your rank requires 157 .\nObtaining Diamonds.\nDiamonds are earned through 7 sources:\nA total of 159 can be obtained through defeating bosses and fulfilling prophecies from the &lt;a href=\"Fated%20List%20of%20Minor%20Prophecies\"&gt;Fated List&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Wretched%20Broker\"&gt;Wretched Broker&lt;/a&gt; can be used to buy Diamonds through: \nOccasionally, 1 can be purchased from &lt;a href=\"Charon\"&gt;Charon's shop&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Styx\"&gt;Temple of Styx&lt;/a&gt; for 1000 (or 800 if Zagreus is in possession of a &lt;a href=\"Loyalty%20Card\"&gt;Loyalty Card&lt;/a&gt;.)\nFinally, 1 may be obtained by &lt;a href=\"Fishing\"&gt;catching&lt;/a&gt; trout, either in &lt;a href=\"Greece\"&gt;Greece&lt;/a&gt; or in the final boss arena, and trading it to the &lt;a href=\"Head%20Chef\"&gt;Head Chef&lt;/a&gt;."}
