{"id": "1708", "revid": "18654", "url": "https://hades.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1708", "title": "Dracon", "text": "Dracons are small, burrowing worm-like entity with the resemblance of the &lt;a href=\"Bone%20Hydra\"&gt;Bone Hydra&lt;/a&gt;. They differ from most enemies in that they do not appear from a summoning circle as other enemies tend to spawn from; instead, they simply appear directly from the ground of &lt;a href=\"Asphodel\"&gt;Asphodel&lt;/a&gt;. This takes much less time than a normal spawn and thus they are some of the first enemies to begin attacking when a new wave begins. Dracons fire an energy projectile off before burrowing elsewhere and repeating the attack. Armored variants fire three volleys before retreating."}
