{"id": "3603", "revid": "3358567", "url": "https://hades.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3603", "title": "Gathering Tools", "text": "Gathering Tools are unlockable equipment used to acquire a number of different recources. Initially, none of the tools are available to use, but after a certain amount of time, the &lt;a href=\"Crescent%20Pick\"&gt;Crescent Pick&lt;/a&gt; will become available for 1. &lt;a href=\"Melino%C3%AB\"&gt;Melino\u00eb&lt;/a&gt; can gather from any resource point once she has unlocked the corresponding Gathering Tool. It is possible to prioritize any available tool in the &lt;a href=\"The%20Crossroads/Training%20Grounds\"&gt;Training Grounds&lt;/a&gt; to make its Resorces appear more often, while resources for Tools that are not prioritized will appear far less often (~1%)."}
{"id": "1056", "revid": "52770468", "url": "https://hades.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1056", "title": "Gemstone", "text": "Gemstones are one of several &lt;a href=\"Artifacts\"&gt;Artifact&lt;/a&gt; currencies that can be found within the Underworld. They can be used to commission upgrades at the &lt;a href=\"House%20Contractor\"&gt;House Contractor&lt;/a&gt;. It's currently the bottom tier artifact in the \"trade up\" tree.\nWith the Brilliant Gemstones upgrade from the &lt;a href=\"House%20Contractor\"&gt;House Contractor&lt;/a&gt;, Gemstones will also drop when collected from a room reward.\nUses.\nGemstones are mainly used for upgrades and decorations at the &lt;a href=\"House%20Contractor\"&gt;House Contractor&lt;/a&gt;, but can also be used for trading at the &lt;a href=\"Wretched%20Broker\"&gt;Wretched Broker&lt;/a&gt;. 32,585 are needed to buy all upgrades at the House Contractor. 4580 is obtained by completing all of the prophecies in the Fated List of Minor Prophecies, so 28005 must be obtained in other fashions to buy all upgrades."}
