{"id": "1684", "revid": "29110118", "url": "https://hades.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1684", "title": "Hermes/Quotes (Hades)", "text": "\"The following is a list of quotes from &lt;a href=\"Hermes\"&gt;Hermes&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Hades%20%28game%29\"&gt;Hades&lt;/a&gt; .\"\nFirst Meeting.\n Zagreus: \n\"A gust of air...\"\n\"This mark, almost like a bat wing. In the name of Hades! Olympus! I accept this message.\"\n Hermes : \n\"Hey boss, found you, good. Hermes, at your service. Pleasure! You are the talk of Olympus! Normally I wouldn't get mixed up, but for you, I will be making an exception. Now, come on, we both got places to be!\"\n Zagreus: \n\"Appreciate the lift, Lord Hermes, sir. Now let's go!\"\nKeepsake Dialogue (&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Lambent Plume&lt;/a&gt;).\nDialogue 01.\n Hermes : \n\"Why, look at you, there, boss! I recognize that fancy plume you got! Just an iota of my speediness in there, but still! Much more than most can do.\"\nDialogue 02 (Maxed).\n Hermes : \n\"Hey looking like you're getting some good use out of that fancy plume of yours! Keep going like that, maybe someday you'll be half as quick as me!\"\nReactions.\nLow Health.\nDialogue 01.\n\"Eugh, I have to tell you, you look awful, Coz. You're barely holding on! Let's see if we can't perk you right back up.\"\nDialogue 02.\n\"Whew, looks like times hit you hard since last we had a run-in, Coz. Well, when life is tough, just hurry through the rubbish bits, I say!\"\nDialogue 03.\n\"Whoa you're a hot mess, there, Coz, what happened getting here? Ah well I hope your travels run a little smoother here on out.\"\nOther Keepsakes.\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Bone Hourglass&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"That's quite a nice Bone Hourglass you got, there, boss. So you're in good with my professional associate, as well. A real gentleman!\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Thunder Signet&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Sorry, boss, my pop had pressing matters to attend to. But I'm here! Relaying you that message, and relaying this.\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Conch Shell&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Here to tell you that Poseidon's on his way, boss. Sometimes he is a little slow. But you'll meet up with him again eventually!\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Owl Pendant&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Expecting someone else, there, boss? A certain half-sister of mine perchance? Well, tough break, I got here first. Want one of these, or not?\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Eternal Rose&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Aphrodite said she's running just a little late, Coz, though I'm sure you understand. Besides, I'm here! In spirit anyhow.\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Blood-Filled Vial&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Soon as I heard you were looking to see Ares, boss, I got here as fast as I could! He's never going to beat me. Much less in all that armor.\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Adamant Arrowhead&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Wanted to let you know my sister Artemis is out looking for you. You should be running into her in any chamber, now!\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Overflowing Cup&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"Afraid that Dionysus couldn't be here for you, boss. Though punctuality has never been one of his stronger suits.\"\n&lt;a href=\"Keepsakes\"&gt;Frostbitten Horn&lt;/a&gt;.\n Hermes : \n\"That chill you were expecting in the air, that wasn't Demeter this time, here, boss! No, that was just me whisking to you in a flash. Makes for a little pleasant breeze I think!\"\nTimer setting active.\nDialogue 01.\n Hermes : \n\"Hah! Can't help but notice you've been timing yourself, boss! Good habit that. Keep an eye on the time, you'll get faster and faster! Not as fast as me, mind.\"\nDialogue 02.\n Hermes : \n\"You know, Coz, since you're timing yourself, case you haven't noticed, doesn't count against you when we stop to have these chats! Insisted on that little rule myself.\"\nBeating personal best.\n Hermes : \n\"Hey you beat your fastest time fighting through all that! Not that I'm keeping track! I'm keeping track.'\"\nMaintaining a streak of successful runs.\n Hermes : \n\"Well look at you, Coz! Rushing to victory after\u00a0 successive victory. Caught wind of your accomplishments down there! Well then, let's keep the streak alive!\"\nHaving the \"Forced Overtime\" &lt;a href=\"Pact%20of%20Punishment\"&gt;Pact of Punishment&lt;/a&gt; active.\n Hermes : \n\"Got all your father's lifeless wretches hot and bothered, going all out all because of that \"Forced Overtime\" condition of his, isn't that right, Coz? Well, if they're interested in getting things done quickly, I am sure you can oblige them in a bit!\"\nGeneric Greetings.\nDialogue 01.\n Hermes : \n\"Hey, uh, could you do a little favor for me, Coz? My brothers, sisters, family, and whatnot, they are unaware I'm working with you, here. It's no big deal, but let's keep it that way for now. All right?\"\nDialogue 02.\n Hermes : \n\"Message for you boss. It says, 'You're rather slow. If only somebody could help you out with that.' Huh, fancy that, what a coincidence!\"\nDialogue 03.\n Hermes : \n\"Another message for you, Cos, this one says, 'Hey, mate! If you do ever make it up here on this mountaintop for whatever reason, we should hang out, alright? I can show you around.' Your friend, Hermes.\"\nDialogue 04.\n Hermes : \n\"Another message here! It says, 'One small spoon dried oregano, two spoons extra virgin olive oil, one large onion, minced, a dash of salt to taste,' wait, this isn't for you. Though you should try it sometime if you ever make it out!\"\nDialogue 05.\n Hermes : \n\"Package for you, boss, and I think you know what's inside. Well maybe not exactly, but just pick something, will you?\"\nDialogue 06.\n Hermes : \n\"You know, boss, just between us? Out of all special delivery recipients I've had over the ages, here, I've got to say, you're the most interesting one!\"\nDialogue 07.\n Hermes : \n\"Oh, you ready for this, boss? Got you the Premium Express this time. Absolute cream of the crop right here! You're going to go real far.\"\nDialogue 08.\n Hermes : \n\"Guess what, Coz? It's the Premium Express, delivered straight to you, fresh from the richest mountaintop up here! You're going to like this.\"\nDialogue 09.\n Hermes : \n\"You know, Coz, all this time that I've been busing souls across the borders of your father's land, it's good to have the chance to help somebody out the other way!\"\nDialogue 10.\n Hermes : \n\"Happened to be in the area, boss! Seeing as the mortal folk up here keep dying off, and someone's got to\u00a0bring their souls to your domain, now, don't they.\"\nDialogue 11.\n Hermes : \n\"Boss, you probably caught yourself thinking: Hermes sure is quick! So how come it took so long for him to show up in first place? Well, I'm afraid, it's not for you to know. But! It's not because I was late. Not late for anything.\"\nDialogue 12.\n Hermes : \n\"Afraid there's no one faster than myself, here, Coz. But good news is, you are about to close the gap a little bit!\"\nDialogue 13.\n Hermes : \n\"Heard the news you broke your streak of victories of late, boss. Happens, right? You seem the sort to bounce right back, though. Let me help with that!\"\nDialogue 14.\n Hermes : \n\"Last thing I ever want to do is slow you down, boss. So, enough chit-chat. Now pick and go. Go!\"\nDialogue 15.\n Hermes : \n\"Some members of the family up here, I know they haven't helped at all, but just don't take it personal or anything, all right? Think of it this way: You've got more of us getting along and talking properly than I have ever seen!\"\nDialogue 16.\n Hermes : \n\"Come on, Coz, you can do this! And furthermore, I think you can do this rather quick! Now go!\"\nDialogue 17.\n Hermes : \n\"It's you, boss, that's good! But you're standing still! That's bad. Let's get you up and moving about again, all right?\"\nDialogue 18.\n Hermes : \n\"I know you're kind of in a hurry, boss. But let me show you what a real hurry's all about in just 